thread.title_full: eEuroparts.com reviewed by Mike J Songer

author: Mike J Songer
title: Mike J Songer
text: I have always been able to find the correct parts for my vintage and newer Saabs. Having the option to choose from original Saab or quality aftermarket parts provides me with choice on cost. They ship in most cases the same day and my order arrive in 2 days.
